<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="dark">

<head>
    <title>IRC Chat</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/fitting.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div id="messages">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="" id="chat-input" aria-describedby="chat-button">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="chat-button">Send</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal fade" id="formatting-modal" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h5 class="modal-title">Formatting help</h5>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div class="accordion" id="formatting-accordion">
                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#formatting-markdown">
                                        Text formatting
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="formatting-markdown" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#formatting-accordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        <p>This chat supports simple Discord-style formatting. Just type your message normally, then wrap the part you want to style with the matching symbols before sending it.</p>
                                        <ul class="mb-3">
                                            <li><code>**bold**</code> becomes <strong>bold</strong></li>
                                            <li><code>*italic*</code> becomes <em>italic</em></li>
                                            <li><code>~~strike~~</code> becomes <del>strike</del></li>
                                            <li><code>__underline__</code> becomes <u>underline</u></li>
                                            <li><code>~code~</code> shows inline <code>code</code></li>
                                            <li><code>~~~code block~~~</code> creates a larger code block</li>
                                            <li><code>||spoiler||</code> hides text until someone hovers it</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p class="mb-2">Examples:</p>
                                        <ul class="mb-0">
                                            <li><code>Hello **world**</code> makes only <strong>world</strong> bold</li>
                                            <li><code>This is *important*</code> makes <em>important</em> italic</li>
                                            <li><code>My secret is ||hidden||</code> hides the word until hover</li>
                                            <li><code>Use ~npm start~</code> is useful for commands and code words</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#formatting-emojis">
                                        Emojis
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="formatting-emojis" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#formatting-accordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        <p>Emojis are typed by name with colons on both sides. As soon as you finish a valid emoji code, it is replaced live in the input bar.</p>
                                        <ul class="mb-3">
                                            <li>Type <code>:sad:</code> and it changes into the matching emoji automatically</li>
                                            <li>You must include both colons, like <code>:heart:</code></li>
                                            <li>If the name does not exist, the text stays the same</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p class="mb-0">Tip: open the emoji list below if you forget the available names.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#formatting-emoji-list">
                                        Available emojis
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="formatting-emoji-list" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#formatting-accordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        <ul class="mb-0" id="emoji-list"></ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal fade" id="channel-modal" tabindex="-1">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h5 class="modal-title">Switch channel</h5>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <p>Enter the name of the channel you want to switch to:</p>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="channel-input" placeholder="#channelname" />
                        <button class="btn btn-primary mt-3" id="channel-submit-button">Switch</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-BBtl+eGJRgqQAUMxJ7pMwbEyER4l1g+O15P+16Ep7Q9Q+zqX6gSbd85u4mG4QzX+"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/storage.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/history.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/emojis.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/toast.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/chat.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
